revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yankes}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yanke'' is the 22301<sup>st</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1156 individuals. ''Yanke'' is most common among White (94.98%) individuals. ===Anagrams=== * {{anagrams|en|a=aekny|Kanye|Kenya|nakey}}
